  "texts": [
    "For instance, reasoning capabilities can be evaluated using GAIA [57], while collaboration and communication skills can be assessed with RoCoBench [58] particularly for embodied agents.However, publishing detailed agent profiles may inadvertently expose sensitive information about internal models, tools, or strategies.",
    "Therefore, developing privacy-preserving capability registration frameworks is critical to balance transparency with confidentiality.2) Capability Notification of Agents: Beyond static assessments, maintaining up-to-date knowledge of agent capabilities is crucial for real-time capability discovery and effective task orchestration in IoA systems.",
    "Given the dynamic evolution of large model-based agents, IoA should adopt capability notification strategies to ensure continuous synchronization between agents.• Proactive Notifications.",
    "This strategy involves agents autonomously notifying their gateway agents of any changes in their capabilities [7], such as the acquisition of new tools, skills, or model upgrades, to their gateway agents.",
    "• Event-triggered Notifications."
  ]
}